，由最年長的球員荒木提出，在訓練場的白板上寫上了&ldquo;霸氣&rdquo;二字作為自勉的口號。本次比賽，組委會也特意將寫有全體隊員名字和霸氣字樣的應援旗幟掛了出來，就是為了激勵日本隊不畏一眾世界強豪，打出自我的風格。<br />\n<br />\n日媒認為，此前日本隊爆冷贏了塞爾維亞，可謂是這種霸氣精神的最好體現，同時也存在著領先時反而被逆轉等需要改善的問題，&ldquo;進入6強後的比賽，才是真正考驗日本隊的霸氣的時候。&rdquo;（Anemone）"},{"pid":"ece6eea6c63fe4a7b1fa3c9fe3bb34ab2b460727","tid":860371,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"caf973ee79d75b7574b476114e7c31a375fe1818","tid":860371,"uid":52006,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"睇下08年到而家點解會變成咁，明顯係中共同班奶共狗自己搞彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73072cf6232287182df77933a4d7f7e3e9d3db24","tid":860371,"uid":62409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"支持強隊有咩好自豪<br />\n對住中國足球都可以拍手先係愛國既表現"},{"pid":"b8e8b1e4c4da353b5590247c7b54b4ea229e69e2","tid":860371,"uid":142314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"唔知香港對中國，邊個贏佢先拍掌"},{"pid":"f8c5c15869c17a138ad2373a3989c4ec73a84a24","tid":860371,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c55ab1581dd2ae875ee35a6d0a088b10e406c5c","tid":860371,"uid":174420,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"公道啲講當年我地香港人真係拍曬手掌既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"我無拍喎"},{"pid":"9ad858b32f69ea5f64764da6eefa9c338349c24e","tid":860371,"uid":38546,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aArP7XL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaArP7XL.jpg&h=a92ffd6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人有排學"},{"pid":"c026218a286e0d8c9998dd0b4aba1f45aa5c3710","tid":860371,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":